TLS usage :

NuAuth :
A key for nuauth can be created wth the following command :
openssl req -new -x509 -nodes -days 365 -out nuauth.pem -keyout nuauth.pem
By default nuauth searches the certificate : CONFIGDIR/nuauth.pem

